snippet.title: X17 EXCLUSIVE - Vanessa Paradis Arrives In L.A. Amid Amber Heard Pregnancy Reports
snippet.description:
Monday, February 22, 2016 - Vanessa Paradis is dressed casual for air travel as usual as she arrives in Los Angeles, CA amid reports that ex Johnny Depp and new wife Amber Heard are expecting their first child.
